{"tid":672706,"cid":18,"subCid":0,"title":"(宗教)其實神出現嘅時候 我地又可以點肯定佢就係神","createTime":"2018-05-21T08:29:21.000Z","updateTime":"2018-05-21T10:36:13.000Z","uid":153946,"like":1,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":9,"replies":[{"pid":"b69895dc5955abdcbf2a5e9aa8d024287c5e09e6","tid":672706,"uid":153946,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-05-21T08:29:21.000Z","msg":"適用於咩教嘅神<br />\n唔知有冇人提出過呢個問題<br />\n<br />\n假設有班人(e.g:科學家) 日後開發到啲高端科技<br />\ne.g: 將你嘅意識同感知控制住<br />\n<br />\n令到你覺得自己已經被帶到去神前審判<br />\n科技整埋天堂同地獄嘅感覺畀你<br />\n你亦會&ldquo;見&rdquo;到埋其他人<br />\n<br />\n而嗰個&ldquo;神&rdquo;就同你講佢就係神<br />\n<br />\n個科技唔需要影響你嘅reasoning，只控制你嘅感知。<br />\n<br />\n咁人類點肯定到嗰個神係真係一直相信嘅神/or 其他教嘅神/真神，定係科學家整出嚟嘅野<br />\n<br />\n後記: 假設真係有神，佢係啲人被控制住嘅時候再真係整審判<br />\n<br />\n咁你又會點分辨真偽<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/wonder.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"a0fd93e55fbe4a090288d7a4f9cb0bcd8d0705fa","tid":672706,"uid":31314,"like":4,"dislike":8,"score":-4,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-05-21T08:30:54.000Z","msg":"神以前都係人 因為他做左d人做不到既事 <br />\n所以他變成神"},{"pid":"e657a841c0117d51755763cf3fc0a46ac4de40ed","tid":672706,"uid":22622,"like":4,"dislike":3,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-05-21T08:31:09.000Z","msg":"神以前都係人<br />\n不過佢做到人做唔到嘅野<br />\n之後佢就係神"},{"pid":"e124b4b57b144b3ae3542f90589a66627c4ca690","tid":672706,"uid":164351,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-05-21T08:33:53.000Z","msg":"不過神有時都會做番啲人會做既野"},{"pid":"e370cc52d82809a0f8b1d46a8e54868cb76baef1","tid":672706,"uid":78971,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-05-21T08:38:22.000Z","msg":"問佢攞證件睇"},{"pid":"dc557442725858d5f97456e2f5c1df128e5012ad","tid":672706,"uid":153946,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-05-21T08:38:28.000Z","msg":"認真求問<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"081961d8cd6c875a987f049baf5039d753e73cf4","tid":672706,"uid":132458,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-05-21T08:38:59.000Z","msg"